  "text": "\u03ea . An acute increase in [Ca 2\u03e9 ] i produced by aldosterone in cultured smooth muscle cells could also contribute to increased smooth muscle tone [CITATION_1] but cannot be ascribed to NKCC1 because there was no acute stimulation of this transporter by aldosterone.",
  "correct_citation": {
